<div class="main-content" style=" width: 650px;height: 770px; margin: 40px auto;border: 1px solid #D6D6D6;line-height: 1;">
  <div class="main-head" style="height: 110px;padding-left: 50px;padding-top: 30px;position:relative">
    <img src="data:image/png;base64," style="position:absolute;top:0;right:0;left:0;bottom:0;"/>
      <img style="position:relative;" class="logo"
          src="data:image/png;base64,"
          alt="" />
        <h4 class="title" style="position:relative; width: 177px; font-size: 17px;font-family: PingFang SC;font-weight: bold;color: #10E0FF; line-height: 15px;margin: 21px 0 5px;">企业一体化管理领航者</h4>
        <p class="desc" style="position:relative; font-size: 14px;font-family: PingFang SC;font-weight: bold;color: #FFFFFF;line-height: 21px;">数据互联互通 百万用户选择</p>
      </div>
  <div class="main-body" style="padding: 30px 50px;">
    <div class="respect" style=" font-size: 12px;font-weight: bold;color: #333333;line-height: 21px;">尊敬的客户，您好！</div>
    <p class="main-info" style="font-size: 12px;font-weight: 400; color: #333333;line-height: 21px; margin-top: 4px;">
      @InvoiceDate，@InvoiceSeller为您开具了@InvoiceType。<a class="link" style=" color: #006cff; text-decoration: none;" href="@InvoiceUrl">点击下载发票</a>
    </p>
    <div class="custom-info" style=" width: 463px; height: 145px; background: #E8EFF7;margin: 24px 0;padding: 9px 40px;">
      <ul class="info-list" style="  overflow: hidden;padding:0;list-style:none;margin:0;">
        <li class="info-item" style="height: 12px; font-size: 12px;line-height: 1; color: #000000;margin: 17px 0;">
          <span class="info-name">购方名称：</span>
          <span class="info-value" style=" font-weight: bold;">@InvoiceTitle</span>
        </li>
        <li class="info-item" style="height: 12px; font-size: 12px;line-height: 1; color: #000000;margin: 17px 0;">
          <div class="info-inline fixWidth" style="width: 325px;float: left;">
            <span class="info-name">开票日期：</span>
            <span class="info-value" style=" font-weight: bold;">@InvoiceDate</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-inline" style="float: left;">
            <span class="info-name">合计金额：</span>
            <span class="info-value" style=" font-weight: bold;">@InvoiceMoney</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="info-item" style="height: 12px; font-size: 12px;line-height: 1; color: #000000;margin: 17px 0;">
          <div class="info-inline fixWidth" style="width: 325px;float: left;">
            <span class="info-name">发票代码：</span>
            <span class="info-value" style=" font-weight: bold;">@InvoiceCode</span>
          </div>
          <div class="info-inline" style="float: left;">
            <span class="info-name">发票号码：</span>
            <span class="info-value" style=" font-weight: bold;">@InvoiceNo</span>
          </div>
        </li>
        <li class="info-item" style="height: 20px; font-size: 12px;line-height: 1; color: #000000;margin: 17px 0;">
          <span class="info-name">点击链接查看发票：</span><br/>
          <span class="info-value link"   style="font-weight: bold; color: #006cff; text-decoration: none;" href="#">@InvoiceUrl</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    <div class="get-ticket" style=" text-align: center; font-size: 12px; font-weight: 400;color: #000000;line-height: 28px;margin-bottom: 25px;">
      <div class="ticket-code">
        <img src="@InvoiceQRCode"
            alt="" />
        </div>
      <p style="margin-top:10px;">领票二维码</p>
    </div>
    <div class="about-us" style="overflow: hidden;">
      <div class="company-info" style=" float: left;font-size: 12px; line-height: 1;font-weight: 400;color: #000000;">
        <p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom: 10px;">此致 </p>
        <p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom: 10px;">智邦国际，企业管理软件领导品牌</p>
        <p style="margin-top:0;margin-bottom: 10px;">了解更多，请关注智邦国际官网</p>
        <a class="link" style=" color: #006cff; text-decoration: none;" href="#">http://www.zbintel.com</a>
      </div>
      <div class="company-code" style=" float: right;font-size: 10px;line-height: 12px;font-weight: 400;color: #333333;text-align: center;">
        <img src="data:image/png;base64," alt=""/>
          <p style="margin-top: 0;">扫一扫关注</p>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
